content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.46 - Entry of animals in or upon the airport restricted

State Regulations

No person shall enter in or upon any part of the airport
with any animal except a "Guide Dog," one properly confined for shipment, on a
leash or confined in such a manner as to be under control. Notes
